all the mistakes I need to make

16:00.419 --> 16:01.920
for as long as I need to make them.

16:02.671 --> 16:04.548
Is that why you're fucking my dad?

16:04.548 --> 16:06.175
That is exactly why.

16:06.175 --> 16:10.429
