16:13.265 --> 16:15.309
PAIGE:
That was really interesting.

16:16.602 --> 16:17.811
BILL:
What's so interesting?

16:18.478 --> 16:20.272
The fact that we just
had sex in your office?

16:21.356 --> 16:22.608
Well, I didn't wanna meet at my house,

16:22.608 --> 16:24.985
but I had a feeling
that we really needed to meet.

16:24.985 --> 16:27.070
And now I know why.

16:27.988 --> 16:30.115
I thought I was in love with you.

16:30.949 --> 16:31.992
You're not?

16:31.992 --> 16:34.203
No. Isn't that amazing?

16:34.203 --> 16:35.537
