16:41.043 --> 16:44.129
And I think that this is
a really important step for me.

16:44.129 --> 16:45.923
In my divorce process?

16:45.923 --> 16:46.924
Yes, exactly.

16:46.924 --> 16:48.675
Bill, this is really good news.

16:48.675 --> 16:52.513
