What game are these people are playing?

18:13.385 --> 18:14.428
<i>Magic: The Gathering.</i>

18:15.012 --> 18:16.263
Normally I play online,

18:16.263 --> 18:18.724
but, you know, people.

18:19.474 --> 18:20.434
Huh.

18:20.434 --> 18:22.603
