18:24.146 --> 18:25.272
Not people in person.

18:25.814 --> 18:26.648
Yeah.

18:28.066 --> 18:29.026
Hey., Finn?
FINN: Mm-hmm.

18:30.485 --> 18:31.612
You know, I've been thinking,

18:33.238 --> 18:34.281
thinking about your daddy.

18:34.281 --> 18:35.824
- [scoffs] Whoa.
- No, wait.

18:35.824 --> 18:36.700
I--

18:37.326 --> 18:39.244
