what I've never had, right?

18:45.542 --> 18:46.627
EDWIN:
Mm-hmm.

18:46.627 --> 18:48.962
Now people say that
but it's not true, son.

18:48.962 --> 18:50.881
- It's not?
- No, son.

18:51.548 --> 18:54.426
People miss what they love, Finn.

18:54.885 --> 18:55.719
Period.

18:56.720 --> 18:57.930
Whether they know it or not.

18:58.597 --> 19:01.892
