on something very, very special.

19:03.435 --> 19:04.353
You.

19:04.978 --> 19:06.355
Thanks. I guess.

19:06.813 --> 19:07.648
[Finn clears throat]

19:08.649 --> 19:12.736
Uh, so, which one
of these cards can I buy you?

19:12.736 --> 19:13.570
Are you sure?

19:13.570 --> 19:16.532
Come on. Let your grandpa
get you a card, man.

19:16.990 --> 19:18.492
Which one of these cards would

19:19.034 --> 19:21.787
