what you are talking about, son,

19:32.714 --> 19:34.049
but I'll tell you what.

19:34.049 --> 19:36.301
I will get you that card on one condition.

19:36.301 --> 19:37.135
Mm-hmm.

19:37.511 --> 19:38.720
