19:53.944 --> 19:55.404
- You see him in the black beanie?
- Yeah. No, I saw him.

19:55.404 --> 19:58.782
Okay. He looks like
he needs an ass whooping.

19:58.782 --> 19:59.992
Absolutely not.

19:59.992 --> 20:03.787
Hey, I will get you that card
if you go over there and whoop his ass.

20:11.920 --> 20:13.046
How you gonna play it, Finn?

20:13.046 --> 20:14.423
Shh. Grandpa, I need to focus.

20:15.382 --> 20:17.050
How about the one
with the spooky earrings?

20:18.343 --> 20:19.219
No, no, no.

20:19.219 --> 20:20.929
