I've never played before.

20:51.585 --> 20:52.503
[sighs]

20:52.503 --> 20:53.962
Sometimes I just wanna see
what would happen.

20:55.464 --> 20:57.341
You are an interesting cat.

20:58.634 --> 20:59.510
Uh, you know what?

21:01.011 --> 21:03.263
Can you drive?
